title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight -  Airbus H125 helicopter - version 1.2
description:
In this video we look at the 2 updates which the Airbus H125 received after the initial beta version. Besides the graphical enhancements several new functionalities are now added which make the helicopter even more cool to fly with.

If you also want to give this aircraft a try download your own copy from:
https://flightsim.to/file/25212/airbus-h125-helicopter-project
